videos.description: Penn State QB Trace McSorley doesn't let an Indiana defender get in his way as McSorley rushes for a 10-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: McSorley bowls over Indiana defender for TD

videos.description: Freshman punter Blake Gillikin fumbles the snap but makes up for it as he maintains composure picking up the ball, managing to get off a kick.
videos.headline: Penn State punter saves play after fumbling snap

videos.description: Indiana's Mitchell Paige catches the screen pass and then fumbles, Penn State recovers
videos.headline: Penn State forces Indiana fumble

videos.description: Richard Lagow pass complete to Ricky Jones for 5 yds for a TD
videos.headline: R. Lagow pass to R. Jones for 5-yard TD

videos.description: Indiana QB Richard Lagow and RB Devonte Williams aren't on the same page and Williams fumbles, giving Penn State a gift.
videos.headline: Miscommunication leads to Indiana turnover

videos.description: Saquon Barkley run for no gain to the Ind 45
videos.headline: Indiana stops Penn State on 4th down for second time

videos.description: Mitchell Paige run for 5 yds to the PnSt 46 Mitchell Paige fumbled, forced by Shareef Miller, recovered by PnSt Malik Golden
videos.headline: Indiana fumbles for third time

videos.description: Penn State recovers the fumble on the Indiana five-yard line after a punt hits an Indiana player on the foot.
videos.headline: Mistake by Indiana special teams sets up Penn State

videos.description: Trace McSorley pass complete to Chris Godwin for 6 yds for a TD
videos.headline: T. McSorley pass to C. Godwin for 6-yard TD

videos.description: Trace McSorley's pass is intercepted by Indiana's Rashard Fant and returned 26 yards in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Indiana DB makes impressive INT

videos.description: Devine Redding runs for 12 yards to the end zone for a Hoosier touchdown and with the extra point ties Penn State at 14 apiece.
videos.headline: Indiana's Redding finds the end zone for 12-yard TD

videos.description: Indiana head coach Kevin Wilson says his defense is helping Hoosiers overcome first half turnovers
videos.headline: Indiana head coach Kevin Wilson says his defense is helping Hoosiers overcome first half turnovers

videos.description: Penn State head coach James Franklin hopes to get ground game going in second half
videos.headline: Penn State head coach James Franklin hopes to get ground game going in second half

videos.description: Trace McSorley pass intercepted by Tony Fields, return for 16 yds to the PnSt 29
videos.headline: T. McSorley pass intercepted by T. Fields

videos.description: Zander Diamont pass complete to Camion Patrick for 52 yds to the PSU 7 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Deep ball puts Indiana in red zone

videos.description: In the third quarter, Devine Redding runs 6 yards to the end zone for an touchdown to give Indiana a 2-score lead over Penn State.
videos.headline: Hoosiers' Redding rushes up the middle for 6-yard score

videos.description: Penn State WR Saeed Blacknall wrestles Indiana defenders and hauls in a 43-yard pass from Trace McSorley.
videos.headline: Penn State WR comes down with tough catch

videos.description: Trace McSorley connects with Chris Godwin for a 21-yard touchdown to get within three of Indiana.
videos.headline: Penn State narrows the gap with 21-yard strike

videos.description: Penn State's trick play puts the Nittany Lions on the Indiana 3-yard line in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Flea flicker puts Penn State deep in Indiana territory

videos.description: Saquon Barkley scores in the fourth quarter giving Penn State the lead over Indiana.
videos.headline: Barkley puts Penn State in front

videos.description: Nick Westbrook hauls in a 40-yard pass from Richard Lagow to take back the lead from Penn State in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Indiana quickly takes back the lead with 40-yard TD

videos.description: Saquon Barkley bull rushes his way into the end zone to give Penn State the lead once again over Indiana.
videos.headline: Barkley's 2nd TD gives Penn State lead again

videos.description: Torrence Brown recovers an Indiana fumble and takes it to the end zone for a 9-yard touchdown, securing Penn State's win.
videos.headline: Penn State seals game with fumble recovery for TD

videos.description: Penn State head coach James Franklin discusses adjustments after injuries with offensive line in win over Indiana
videos.headline: Penn State head coach James Franklin discusses adjustments after injuries with offensive line in win over Indiana

videos.description: Barkley, Penn State grind out tough win against Indiana
videos.headline: Barkley, Penn State grind out tough win against Indiana

videos.description: Saquon Barkley ran for two touchdowns in the fourth quarter as Penn State came back to beat Indiana 45-31.
